These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Flower: zinnia, dahlia, amaryllis, poppy
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Flower:dahlia##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Flower:zinnia##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Flower:dahlia is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Flower:amaryllis##1
6. Flower:dahlia is somewhere to the left of Flower:zinnia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Flower      | amaryllis  | dahlia | poppy        | zinnia |

