2. Job:doctor is somewhere to the left of Job:accountant##5
3. Job:doctor is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. Job:manager is on the left of Job:doctor##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Job     | coach | manager       | doctor         | accountant     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

